{"type":null,"faqId":37089,"title":"睡眠质量如何评判？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:microsoft yahei;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>从手环APP上统计的深睡时间可以评判您的睡眠质量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>深睡时间 ≤ 1小时：睡眠质量差</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1小时 &lt; 深睡时间 &lt; 3小时：睡眠质量一般</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、  </span><span>深睡时间 ≥ 3小时：睡眠质量好</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、  </span><span class=\"s2\">在深睡眠期，是睡得比较沉，人处于全身心放松的状态，身体动作会比较少；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3、  </span><span class=\"s2\">浅睡眠是浅层的放松，外部的一点小动静人就会醒了，身体动作会相对比较多；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4、  </span><span class=\"s2\">深睡和浅睡是根据你晚上的睡眠时的加速度波形的波动大小决定的，在一个睡眠周期内波动比较多时处于浅睡状态，波动较少时处于深睡状态</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2253","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":110,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,睡眠质量,睡眠","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}